 <id>0811.3666</id><submitter>Radu Stancu M.</submitter><version version='v1'><date>Sat, 22 Nov 2008 08:11:07 GMT</date><size>16kb</size></version><title>A characteristic subgroup for fusion systems</title><authors>Silvia Onofrei, Radu Stancu</authors><categories>math.RT math.GR</categories><comments>LaTeX file, 19 pages</comments><msc-class>20D15, 20E25</msc-class><journal-ref>Journal of Algebra 322 (2009) 1705-1718</journal-ref><doi>10.1016/j.jalgebra.2009.05.026</doi><license>http://arxiv.org/licenses/nonexclusive-distrib/1.0/</license><abstract>  As a counterpart for the prime 2 to Glauberman's $ZJ$-theorem, Stellmacher
