  (Johannes Gutenberg University Mainz)</authors><categories>hep-ph</categories><comments>11 pages, 3 figures</comments><report-no>MZ-TH/08-33</report-no><journal-ref>Phys.Rev.D79:076001,2009</journal-ref><doi>10.1103/PhysRevD.79.076001</doi><license>http://arxiv.org/licenses/nonexclusive-distrib/1.0/</license><abstract>  A detailed phenomenological analysis of neutral kaon mixing in &quot;little
