 <id>0811.3688</id><submitter>Gerardo Cristofano</submitter><version version='v1'><date>Mon, 24 Nov 2008 14:25:43 GMT</date><size>51kb</size></version><title>A general CFT model for antiferromagnetic spin-1/2 ladders with Mobius
  boundary conditions</title><authors>Gerardo Cristofano, Vincenzo Marotta, Adele Naddeo, Giuliano Niccoli</authors><categories>hep-th</categories><comments>23 pages, 5 figures; J. Stat. Mech.: Theory Exp. (2008), in print</comments><journal-ref>J.Stat.Mech.0812:P12010,2008</journal-ref><doi>10.1088/1742-5468/2008/12/P12010</doi><license>http://arxiv.org/licenses/nonexclusive-distrib/1.0/</license><abstract>  We show how the low-energy properties of the 2-leg XXZ spin-1/2 ladders with
