  2. Additional comments are welcomed</comments><journal-ref>Phys. Rev. Lett. 103, 110502 (2009)</journal-ref><doi>10.1103/PhysRevLett.103.110502</doi><license>http://arxiv.org/licenses/nonexclusive-distrib/1.0/</license><abstract>  For manipulations of multipartite quantum systems, it was well known that all
