 <id>0811.3767</id><submitter>Mukul Laad S</submitter><version version='v1'><date>Sun, 23 Nov 2008 18:46:28 GMT</date><size>11kb</size></version><title>On Field-Induced Quantum Criticality in YbRh_{2}Si_[2}</title><authors>M. S. Laad</authors><categories>cond-mat.str-el</categories><comments>4++ pages, submitted to Phys. Rev. Lett</comments><license>http://arxiv.org/licenses/nonexclusive-distrib/1.0/</license><abstract>  The quantum critical point (QCP) in $YbRh_{2}Si_{2}$ is an enigma for the
