 <id>0811.3825</id><submitter>Pavel Stovicek</submitter><version version='v1'><date>Mon, 24 Nov 2008 09:18:30 GMT</date><size>272kb</size></version><title>On the Spectrum of a Quantum Dot with Impurity in the Lobachevsky Plane</title><authors>P. Stovicek, M. Tusek</authors><categories>math-ph math.MP</categories><comments>Proceedings of the 7th Workshop on Operator Theory in Krein Spaces</comments><license>http://arxiv.org/licenses/nonexclusive-distrib/1.0/</license><abstract>  A model of a quantum dot with impurity in the Lobachevsky plane is
