 <id>0811.3844</id><submitter>Wojciech Krolikowski</submitter><version version='v1'><date>Mon, 24 Nov 2008 11:23:40 GMT</date><size>8kb</size></version><title>Hidden-sector fermions in two or three generations</title><authors>Wojciech Krolikowski</authors><categories>hep-ph</categories><comments>10 pages</comments><report-no>IFT-08/13</report-no><license>http://arxiv.org/licenses/nonexclusive-distrib/1.0/</license><abstract>  We recall the argument based both on Dirac's square root procedure and an
