 <id>0811.3851</id><submitter>Martin Simson</submitter><version version='v1'><date>Mon, 24 Nov 2008 12:23:45 GMT</date><size>73kb</size></version><title>Measuring the proton spectrum in neutron decay - latest results with
  aSPECT</title><authors>M. Simson, F. Ayala Guardia, S. Bae{\ss}ler, M. Borg, F. Gl\&quot;uck, W.
  Heil, I. Konorov, G. Konrad, R. Mu\~noz Horta, K.K.H. Leung, Yu. Sobolev, T.
  Soldner, H.-F. Wirth, O. Zimmer</authors><categories>nucl-ex</categories><comments>Accepted for publication in the Conference Proceedings of the
  International Workshop on Particle Physics with Slow Neutrons 2008 held at
