  Finite Groups</title><authors>Roland L\&quot;otscher</authors><categories>math.AG math.RT</categories><comments>34 pages, no figures</comments><msc-class>14R20; 14L30; 20C20</msc-class><license>http://arxiv.org/licenses/nonexclusive-distrib/1.0/</license><abstract>  We investigate essential dimension of finite groups over arbitrary fields and
