the unit ball is valid also for a local automorphism $f$ of a pseudoellipsoid
$\E^n_{(p_1, ..., p_{k})} \= \{z \in \C^n : \sum_{j= 1}^{n - k}|z_j|^2 +
|z_{n-k+1}|^{2 p_1} + ... + |z_n|^{2 p_{k}} &lt; 1 \}$, provided that $f$ is
