  distribution of Levy type</title><authors>H.E. Roman, R.A. Siliprandi, C. Dose, C. Riccardi, and M. Porto</authors><categories>q-fin.GN</categories><comments>6 pages, 6 figures</comments><doi>10.1209/0295-5075/84/68003</doi><license>http://arxiv.org/licenses/nonexclusive-distrib/1.0/</license><abstract>  We analyze annual revenues and earnings data for the 500 largest-revenue U.S.
