  GKS-Lindblad Generators as Lie Wedge</title><authors>G. Dirr, U. Helmke, I. Kurniawan, and T. Schulte-Herbrueggen</authors><categories>quant-ph math-ph math.MP math.OC</categories><comments>As accepted for &quot;Reports on Mathematical Physics&quot;: includes new
