  Hirano, and H. Hosono</authors><categories>cond-mat.supr-con</categories><journal-ref>Phys. Rev. Lett. 102, 117004 (2009)</journal-ref><doi>10.1103/PhysRevLett.102.117004</doi><license>http://arxiv.org/licenses/nonexclusive-distrib/1.0/</license><abstract>  The temperature and angular dependence of the upper critical field (Hc2) is
