 <id>0811.4014</id><submitter>Michael Galperin</submitter><version version='v1'><date>Tue, 25 Nov 2008 04:51:46 GMT</date><size>120kb</size></version><title>Transport in molecular states language: Generalized quantum master
  equation approach</title><authors>Massimiliano Esposito and Michael Galperin</authors><categories>cond-mat.mes-hall cond-mat.mtrl-sci</categories><comments>10 pages, 3 figures</comments><journal-ref>Phys. Rev. B 79, 205303 (2009)</journal-ref><doi>10.1103/PhysRevB.79.205303</doi><license>http://arxiv.org/licenses/nonexclusive-distrib/1.0/</license><abstract>  A simple scheme capable of treating transport in molecular junctions in the
