  energy, from the holographic principle</title><authors>L. N. Granda</authors><categories>gr-qc</categories><comments>21 pages, 18 figures, 2 tables</comments><journal-ref>Int.J.Mod.Phys.D18 2009:1749-1764,2009</journal-ref><doi>10.1142/S0218271809015291</doi><license>http://arxiv.org/licenses/nonexclusive-distrib/1.0/</license><abstract>  We propose an holographic quintessence and tachyon models of dark energy. The
