  of Quenched Traps: Subdiffusion</title><authors>I. M. Sokolov, S. B. Yuste, J. J. Ruiz-Lorenzo, and Katja Lindenberg</authors><categories>cond-mat.stat-mech cond-mat.dis-nn</categories><comments>9 pages, 3 figures</comments><journal-ref>Phys. Rev. E 79, 051113 (2009).</journal-ref><license>http://arxiv.org/licenses/nonexclusive-distrib/1.0/</license><abstract>  We present a mean field model for coagulation ($A+A\to A$) and annihilation
