 <id>0811.4185</id><submitter>Ulrich Raitzsch</submitter><version version='v1'><date>Tue, 25 Nov 2008 23:42:05 GMT</date><size>562kb</size></version><title>Investigation of dephasing rates in an interacting Rydberg gas</title><authors>U. Raitzsch, R. Heidemann, H. Weimer, V. Bendkowsky, B. Butscher, P.
  Kollmann, R. L\&quot;ow, H. P. B\&quot;uchler, T. Pfau</authors><categories>quant-ph</categories><comments>13 pages, 5 figures</comments><journal-ref>New Journal of Physics 11 (2009) 055014 (13pp)</journal-ref><doi>10.1088/1367-2630/11/5/055014</doi><license>http://arxiv.org/licenses/nonexclusive-distrib/1.0/</license><abstract>  We experimentally and theoretically investigate the dephasing rates of the
