 <id>0811.4186</id><submitter>Aleksandar Bradic M</submitter><version version='v1'><date>Tue, 25 Nov 2008 23:11:55 GMT</date><size>231kb</size><source_type>D</source_type></version><title>Search Result Clustering via Randomized Partitioning of Query-Induced
  Subgraphs</title><authors>Aleksandar Bradic</authors><categories>cs.IR cs.DS</categories><comments>16th Telecommunications Forum TELFOR 2008</comments><acm-class>H.3.3; I.1.2; E.1; G.3</acm-class><license>http://arxiv.org/licenses/nonexclusive-distrib/1.0/</license><abstract>  In this paper, we present an approach to search result clustering, using
