 <arXivRaw xsi:schemaLocation='http://arxiv.org/OAI/arXivRaw/ http://arxiv.org/OAI/arXivRaw.xsd' xmlns='http://arxiv.org/OAI/arXivRaw/' xmlns:xsi='http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance'>
 <id>0811.4194</id><submitter>Kirill Pushkin</submitter><version version='v1'><date>Wed, 26 Nov 2008 00:52:45 GMT</date><size>994kb</size></version><title>Measurements of W-value, Mobility and Gas Gain in Electronegative
  Gaseous CS2 and CS2 Gas Mixtures</title><authors>Kirill Pushkin and Daniel Snowden-Ifft</authors><categories>physics.ins-det physics.chem-ph</categories><journal-ref>Nucl.Instrum.Meth.A606:569-577,2009</journal-ref><doi>10.1016/j.nima.2009.04.045</doi><license>http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/3.0/</license><abstract>  W-value, mobility and gas gain measurements have been carried out in
