 <arXivRaw xsi:schemaLocation='http://arxiv.org/OAI/arXivRaw/ http://arxiv.org/OAI/arXivRaw.xsd' xmlns='http://arxiv.org/OAI/arXivRaw/' xmlns:xsi='http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance'>
 <id>0811.4196</id><submitter>Masashi Wakamatsu</submitter><version version='v1'><date>Wed, 26 Nov 2008 01:02:02 GMT</date><size>112kb</size></version><version version='v2'><date>Fri, 16 Jan 2009 06:25:06 GMT</date><size>118kb</size></version><title>Chiral-odd generalized parton distributions, transversity decomposition
  of angular momentum, and tensor charges of the nucleon</title><authors>M. Wakamatsu</authors><categories>hep-ph hep-ex nucl-ex</categories><comments>version to appear in Phys. Rev. D</comments><report-no>OU-HET-619</report-no><journal-ref>Phys.Rev.D79:014033,2009</journal-ref><doi>10.1103/PhysRevD.79.014033</doi><license>http://arxiv.org/licenses/nonexclusive-distrib/1.0/</license><abstract>  The forward limit of the chiral-odd generalized parton distributions (GPDs)
