  transition of a suspension of particles with hard sphere-like interactions</title><authors>W. van Megen, V. A. Martinez and G. Bryant</authors><categories>cond-mat.soft cond-mat.stat-mech</categories><comments>9 pages, 4 figures</comments><license>http://arxiv.org/licenses/nonexclusive-distrib/1.0/</license><abstract>  By combining aspects of the coherent and self intermediate scattering
