  coexisting spin and charge fluctuations</title><authors>Hirohito Aizawa, Kazuhiko Kuroki, Takehito Yokoyama, Yukio Tanaka</authors><categories>cond-mat.supr-con</categories><comments>5 pages, 5 figures. To be published in Phys. Rev. Lett</comments><journal-ref>Phys. Rev. Lett. 102, 016403 (2009)</journal-ref><doi>10.1103/PhysRevLett.102.016403</doi><license>http://arxiv.org/licenses/nonexclusive-distrib/1.0/</license><abstract>  We study the Fulde-Ferrell-Larkin-Ovchinnikov (FFLO) state of spin
