  Method</title><authors>Mitchell Luskin and Christoph Ortner</authors><categories>math.NA</categories><comments>20 pages, 2 figures</comments><msc-class>65N30, 65N15, 70C20</msc-class><journal-ref>SIAM. J. Numer. Anal., 47:3070-3086, 2009</journal-ref><license>http://arxiv.org/licenses/nonexclusive-distrib/1.0/</license><abstract>  We investigate two examples of node-based cluster summation rules that have
