 <id>0811.4244</id><submitter>Vakhtang Rostiashvili</submitter><version version='v1'><date>Wed, 26 Nov 2008 08:28:08 GMT</date><size>63kb</size></version><title>Polymer desorption under pulling: a novel dichotomic phase transition</title><authors>S. Bhattacharya, V. G. Rostiashvili, A. Milchev, T.A. Vilgis</authors><categories>cond-mat.soft cond-mat.stat-mech</categories><comments>10 pages, 4 figures</comments><journal-ref>Phys. Rev. E 79, 030802(R) (2009)</journal-ref><doi>10.1103/PhysRevE.79.030802</doi><license>http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/3.0/</license><abstract>  We show that the structural properties and phase behavior of a self-avoiding
