  Kolmogorov exponent 4/3</comments><journal-ref>Phys.Lett.B681:362-366,2009</journal-ref><doi>10.1016/j.physletb.2009.10.032</doi><license>http://arxiv.org/licenses/nonexclusive-distrib/1.0/</license><abstract>  Kolmogorov wave turbulence plays an important role for the thermalization
