 <id>0811.4297</id><submitter>Miodrag Krmar</submitter><version version='v1'><date>Wed, 26 Nov 2008 13:12:00 GMT</date><size>3kb</size></version><title>Generalized Laplace Method for Simple Determination of Kerr-Newman Black
  Hole Horizon Radius</title><authors>Vladan Pankovic, Sima Ciganovic, Jovan Ivanovic</authors><categories>gr-qc</categories><comments>4 pages, no figures</comments><report-no>Ph-19/11-08</report-no><license>http://arxiv.org/licenses/nonexclusive-distrib/1.0/</license><abstract>  In this work we present a generalized Laplace method for a formal, simple,
