 <id>0811.4318</id><submitter>C T J Dodson</submitter><version version='v1'><date>Wed, 26 Nov 2008 14:12:27 GMT</date><size>1643kb</size><source_type>D</source_type></version><version version='v2'><date>Fri, 22 May 2009 10:09:23 GMT</date><size>1660kb</size><source_type>D</source_type></version><title>On the entropy flows to disorder</title><authors>C.T.J. Dodson</authors><categories>math-ph math.MP</categories><comments>Enlarged version of original. 11 pages, 6 figures, 15 references</comments><msc-class>82-08; 15A52</msc-class><license>http://arxiv.org/licenses/nonexclusive-distrib/1.0/</license><abstract>  Gamma distributions, which contain the exponential as a special case, have a
