 <id>0811.4323</id><submitter>Pavel Grigoriev</submitter><version version='v1'><date>Wed, 26 Nov 2008 14:36:09 GMT</date><size>251kb</size></version><title>Magnetic Field Induced Coherence-Incoherence Crossover in the Interlayer
  Conductivity of a Layered Organic Metal</title><authors>M. V. Kartsovnik, P. D. Grigoriev, W. Biberacher, N. D. Kushch</authors><categories>cond-mat.mes-hall cond-mat.supr-con</categories><comments>5 pages</comments><license>http://arxiv.org/licenses/nonexclusive-distrib/1.0/</license><abstract>  The angle-dependent interlayer magnetoresistance of the layered organic metal
