 <id>0811.4341</id><submitter>Radu Ioan Bot</submitter><version version='v1'><date>Wed, 26 Nov 2008 15:18:21 GMT</date><size>15kb</size></version><title>Enlargements of positive sets</title><authors>Radu Ioan Bot, Erno Robert Csetnek</authors><categories>math.OC math.FA</categories><comments>16 pages</comments><msc-class>47H05, 46N10, 42A50</msc-class><journal-ref>Journal of Mathematical Analysis and Applications (2009), 356 (1),
  328-337</journal-ref><doi>10.1016/j.jmaa.2009.03.028</doi><license>http://arxiv.org/licenses/nonexclusive-distrib/1.0/</license><abstract>  In this paper we introduce the notion of enlargement of a positive set in SSD
