 <id>0811.4361</id><submitter>Jean-Louis Verger-Gaugry</submitter><version version='v1'><date>Wed, 26 Nov 2008 16:19:09 GMT</date><size>41kb</size></version><title>On the spectrum of the Thue-Morse quasicrystal and the rarefaction
