 <id>0811.4522</id><submitter>Lenny Taelman</submitter><version version='v1'><date>Thu, 27 Nov 2008 12:30:27 GMT</date><size>15kb</size></version><title>Special L-values of t-motives: a conjecture</title><authors>Lenny Taelman</authors><categories>math.NT math.AG</categories><comments>in International Mathematics Research Notices (2009)</comments><msc-class>11G09</msc-class><journal-ref>Int. Math. Res. Not. (2009), article ID rnp038</journal-ref><doi>10.1093/imrn/rnp038</doi><license>http://arxiv.org/licenses/nonexclusive-distrib/1.0/</license><abstract>  We propose a conjecture on special values of $ L $-functions in a function
