 <id>0811.4547</id><submitter>Umut Adem</submitter><version version='v1'><date>Thu, 27 Nov 2008 14:09:50 GMT</date><size>166kb</size></version><title>Anomaly in Nonlinear Magnetoelectric Response of YbMnO3</title><authors>U. Adem, M. Mostovoy, N. Bellido, A. A. Nugroho, Ch. Simon, and T. T.
  M. Palstra</authors><categories>cond-mat.mtrl-sci</categories><license>http://arxiv.org/licenses/nonexclusive-distrib/1.0/</license><abstract>  We observe a seemingly complex magnetic field dependence of dielectric
