  Surnev, F.P. Netzer</authors><categories>cond-mat.mtrl-sci</categories><comments>24 pages, 12 figures</comments><journal-ref>J. Phys.: Condens. Matter 21 (13), 134008 (2009)</journal-ref><doi>10.1088/0953-8984/21/13/134008</doi><license>http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/3.0/</license><abstract>  Two-dimensional manganese oxide layers have been grown on Pd(100) and have
