 <id>0811.4615</id><submitter>Zsuzsanna Dancso</submitter><version version='v1'><date>Thu, 27 Nov 2008 21:30:26 GMT</date><size>346kb</size></version><version version='v2'><date>Wed, 3 Dec 2008 20:17:35 GMT</date><size>346kb</size></version><version version='v3'><date>Fri, 14 Jan 2011 21:02:35 GMT</date><size>352kb</size></version><title>On the Kontsevich integral for knotted trivalent graphs</title><authors>Zsuzsanna Dancso</authors><categories>math.GT math.QA</categories><comments>Journal version, 47 pages</comments><msc-class>57M25, 57M27, 57M15, 05C10</msc-class><journal-ref>Algebraic and Geometric Topology 10 (2010) 1317--1365</journal-ref><license>http://arxiv.org/licenses/nonexclusive-distrib/1.0/</license><abstract>  We construct an extension of the Kontsevich integral of knots to knotted
